["Maksim Andreyevich Shirokov (Russian: \u041c\u0430\u043a\u0441\u0438\u043c \u0410\u043d\u0434\u0440\u0435\u0435\u0432\u0438\u0447 \u0428\u0438\u0440\u043e\u043a\u043e\u0432 ; born 26 March 1994) is a Russian football forward. He plays for FC Saturn Ramenskoye.","He made his debut in the Russian Second Division for FC Rusichi Oryol on 23 May 2012 in a game against FC Spartak Tambov.[1]","He made his Russian Football National League debut for FC Khimki on 21 August 2016 in a game against FC Sokol Saratov.","This biographical article related to a Russian association football midfielder born in 1994 is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]